  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 425°F (220°C).",
    "In a large bowl, toss the grape tomatoes, onion, garlic, carrots, and celery with olive oil, thyme, salt, and pepper until they are evenly coated.",
    "Spread the mixture on the bottom and sides of a 12-inch terracotta dish, leaving a little space at the top.",
    "Roast in the preheated oven for 25 minutes or until the vegetables are tender and lightly browned."
